Title: KitchenAid Stand Mixer — The Icon
Author: wavelet-director

INT. SUNLIT HOME KITCHEN - MORNING

A pat of golden butter and a cascade of white sugar drop into a heavy white ceramic mixing bowl. The flat beater begins to turn, catching the warm morning light.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - CONTINUOUS

A pristine cream-white tilt-head stand mixer sits on a marble counter in profile. The tilt-head slowly lowers into the bowl, locking down with quiet authority.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - CONTINUOUS

Macro: the spiral dough hook rotates, pulling a smooth ball of dough into shape against the inside wall of the polished steel bowl.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - CONTINUOUS

A waterfall of dark chocolate chips pours into the bowl from above, bouncing off the spinning paddle as pale cookie dough catches them.

CUT TO:

INT. STUDIO - CONTINUOUS

The KitchenAid wordmark holds on a clean cream background. A red button reads SHOP THE STAND MIXER.

FADE OUT.
